title: *OCE* LOOKING FOR DUO PARTNER
body: I'm looking for a duo partner who knows how to support or adc well. Im currently silver 3 and have been so close to gold repeatedly. I need another who isnt toxic, is positive and knows what they are doing around the same rank or high (preferably) Please add me, my summoner name is LngIslandIceTito

replies.body: Hey dude Added bit late but if u want to grind the last 2 days i can help you out
